items.name: windows95portfolio
items.description: This project is a fully interactive Windows-95–style portfolio built using Next.js, React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS. It recreates the classic desktop experience with draggable windows, a functional Start Menu, retro UI elements, and a complete suite of mini-games like Minesweeper, Chess, Tetris, Solitaire, and Pong.
